1. System Architecture Requirements
  Overall Architecture.
  Microservices-based architecture for scalability and maintainability.
  RESTful API design following OpenAPI 3.0 specifications.
  Mobile-first approach with responsive web admin panel.
  Real-time capabilities using WebSocket connections for live updates.
  Cloud-native deployment with containerization support.

