-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
2. Functional Requirements
2.1 User Management
  Multi-role authentication (Customer, Service Provider, Admin)
  Phone number-based registration with OTP verification
  Social login integration (Google, Facebook optional)
  Profile management with image upload capabilities
  Address management supporting multiple saved addresses
  User verification system for service providers

2.2 Service Discovery & Management
  Location-based service search within configurable radius (2-10 km)
  Category-wise service browsing with 8 main categories
Real-time provider availability status updates
Advanced filtering (price, rating, distance, availability)
Service provider profiles with photos, reviews, experience
Dynamic pricing support (fixed, hourly, per-sqft, negotiable)

2.3 Booking System
Multi-step booking flow with date/time selection
Calendar integration showing provider availability
Booking confirmation with SMS/email notifications
Real-time booking status tracking (pending → confirmed → completed)
Reschedule/cancellation with policy enforcement
Special instructions and requirement capture

2.4 Payment System
Multiple payment methods (UPI, Credit/Debit Card, Net Banking, Cash)
Razorpay integration for online payments
Split payment logic (platform commission + provider amount)
Automatic refund processing for cancellations
Payment receipt generation and email delivery
Wallet system for storing credits/cashback

2.5 Rating & Review System
Post-service rating (1-5 stars) with comments
Photo upload in reviews for authenticity
Review moderation to prevent fake reviews
Aggregate rating calculation for providers
Review response capability for service providers

2.6 Communication System
In-app messaging between customers and providers
Push notifications for booking updates
SMS notifications for critical updates
Real-time status updates via WebSocket
Customer support chat integration

3. Non-Functional Requirements
3.1 Performance Requirements
API response time: < 500ms for 95% of requests
App loading time: < 3 seconds for initial load
Database query optimization: < 100ms for location-based searches
Image compression: Automatic resizing and optimization
Concurrent users: Support 1000+ simultaneous users
Search results: Display within 2 seconds

3.2 Scalability Requirements
Horizontal scaling capability for backend services
Database sharding support for geographic distribution
CDN integration for image and static content delivery
Auto-scaling based on traffic patterns
Load balancing across multiple server instances

3.3 Security Requirements
JWT token authentication with refresh token mechanism
API rate limiting to prevent abuse
Data encryption in transit (HTTPS) and at rest
PII data protection following Indian data privacy laws
SQL injection prevention using parameterized queries
XSS and CSRF protection for web components
Secure payment processing with PCI DSS compliance

3.4 Reliability Requirements
99.5% uptime service level agreement
Automatic failover for critical services
Database backup every 4 hours with point-in-time recovery
Error logging and monitoring with alert system
Graceful degradation when services are unavailable


5.1 Payment Gateway Integration
Primary: Razorpay for comprehensive payment solutions
UPI Integration: Direct UPI payment processing
Webhook handling for payment status updates
Refund API integration for automated refunds
Payment analytics and reporting capabilities

5.3 Communication Services
SMS Gateway: TextLocal/MSG91 for OTP and notifications
Email Service: SendGrid/Amazon SES for transactional emails
Push Notifications: Firebase Cloud Messaging (FCM)
WhatsApp Business API: For customer support (future)

5.4 File Storage & CDN
Image storage: AWS S3/DigitalOcean Spaces
CDN distribution: CloudFlare for fast content delivery
Image optimization: Automatic compression and resizing
Backup strategy: Multi-region redundancy

7.2 Real-time Requirements
WebSocket connections for live booking updates
Push notification delivery within 5 seconds
Real-time provider location tracking during service
Live chat messaging between users

8. Security & Compliance Requirements
8.1 Data Protection
GDPR compliance for user data handling
Indian IT Act compliance for local regulations
PII data encryption using AES-256
Secure API endpoints with proper authentication
Regular security audits and penetration testing

8.2 Payment Security
PCI DSS Level 1 compliance for payment processing
Tokenization of sensitive payment data
3D Secure authentication for card payments
Fraud detection mechanisms
Secure webhook verification for payment callbacks

9. Monitoring & Analytics Requirements
9.1 Application Monitoring
Real-time error tracking with Sentry/Bugsnag
Performance monitoring for API response times
User behavior analytics with custom events
Business metrics dashboard for key performance indicators

9.2 Business Analytics
Booking conversion rates tracking
Provider performance metrics monitoring
Revenue analytics with commission calculations
Customer retention analysis and churn prediction
Market penetration reports for different Pune areas
